        <TextItem
                 Text="Introduction"
                 Size="1.0"
                 Position="500.0 470.0" />
        <TextItem
                 Text="For thousands of years, people of planet Xen have colonized the"
                 Position="500.0 410.0" />
        <TextItem
                 Text="planets in their galaxy. As time went by, many colonies grew"
                 Position="500.0 370.0" />
        <TextItem
                 Text="unhappy about their status, as everything was controlled by Xen."
                 Position="500.0 330.0" />
        <TextItem
                 Text="Some of them organized military units and declared independence."
                 Position="500.0 290.0" />
        <TextItem
                 Text="Beside the raging war between Xen Empire and the rebels there"
                 Position="500.0 230.0" />
        <TextItem
                 Text="is increased activity of alien species, who destroy human ships."
                 Position="500.0 190.0" />

        <Menu
             Text="Continue"
             Info="Start a new game!"
             Position="500.0 110.0">
            <TextItem
                    Text="Chapter One: The Pursuit"
                    Size="1.0"
                    Position="500.0 470.0" />
            <TextItem
                    Text="One day, while wandering on abandoned planet you found a"
                    Position="500.0 430.0" />
            <TextItem
                    Text="beautiful crystal. You took it hoping to sell it for a good price."
                    Position="500.0 390.0" />
            <TextItem
                    Text="On the way, you were attacked by two pirates who looted"
                    Position="500.0 330.0" />
            <TextItem
                    Text="your ship and took the crystal. You bearly managed to stay alive."
                    Position="500.0 290.0" />
            <TextItem
                    Text="Today, your escape pod reached a nearby planet. You learned that"
                    Position="500.0 230.0" />
            <TextItem
                    Text="pirates come from planet Torres and decided to go after them."
                    Position="500.0 190.0" />

            <ActionItem
                Text="Begin Chapter One"
                Action="NewCampaign"
                Info="Start a new game!"
                Position="500.0 110.0"/>
        </Menu>
    </Menu>

